        "subject": "SGI-220 llite: only root can set FS default stripe",
        "message": "SGI-220 llite: only root can set FS default stripe\n\nCurrently client doesn't check permission before updating filesystem\ndefault stripe on MGS, which isn't secure and obvious.\n\nSince we setattr on MDS first, and then set default stripe on MGS,\nwe can just return error upon setattr failure.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: If65a82351ae3e0ff30da46236ee67eb9d083aac2\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_5"
    }
